---
title: Harissa Halloumi Rainbow Bowls with Garlic-Hummus Dressing
description: Delicious halloumi slices coated in spicy harissa – that's how we're changing the simple salad game! Basmati rice is topped with a flurry of colourful veggies, all tossed in a homemade garlic-hummus dressing. Each bite of this salad is an explosion of flavour that will satisfy your tastebuds and your appetite!
